<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQ - CryptoInfoHub</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset default margins and paddings */
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        /* Body styles */
        
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f5ff;
            /* Light blue background */
            color: #333;
            /* Dark grey text color */
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        /* Header styles */
        
        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        header h1 {
            color: #007bff;
            /* Blue heading color */
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        /* Main section styles */
        
        main {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        /* FAQ section styles */
        
        #faq {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            /* White background for FAQ section */
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            /* Soft shadow effect */
        }
        
        #faq h2 {
            color: #007bff;
            /* Blue heading color */
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        /* Article styles */
        
        article {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        article h3 {
            color: #0056b3;
            /* Dark blue heading color */
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        article p {
            color: #666;
            /* Medium grey text color */
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        article a {
            color: #007bff;
            /* Blue link color */
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        article a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section id="faq">
            <h2>FAQ</h2>
            <article>
                <h3>What is CryptoInfoHub?</h3>
                <p>CryptoInfoHub is a platform designed to provide comprehensive and real-time information about various cryptocurrencies. It offers live ticker data, order book visualization, and detailed cryptocurrency information to help users stay informed
                    and make better trading decisions.</p>
            </article>
            <article>
                <h3>How do I use the live ticker data feature?</h3>
                <p>To use the live ticker data feature, simply enter the cryptocurrency ticker symbol in the form provided on the homepage and click the "Submit" button. You will receive real-time data including the symbol, 24-hour price, volume, and last
                    trade price.</p>
            </article>
            <article>
                <h3>What information is displayed in the order book visualization?</h3>
                <p>The order book visualization displays bids and asks data for a specified cryptocurrency ticker symbol. This includes bid prices, quantities, and numbers, as well as ask prices, quantities, and numbers. It helps users understand the current
                    market depth and trading sentiment.</p>
            </article>
            <article>
                <h3>What detailed information can I get about a cryptocurrency?</h3>
                <p>By entering a cryptocurrency ticker symbol, you can access detailed information such as base currency, counter currency, minimum price increment, minimum order size, maximum order size, lot size, status, auction details, and imbalance.
                    This comprehensive data aids in making informed trading decisions.</p>
            </article>
            <article>
                <h3>Is the data on CryptoInfoHub updated in real-time?</h3>
                <p>Yes, the data on CryptoInfoHub is fetched from the blockchain API and is updated in real-time to provide the most accurate and current information about cryptocurrencies.</p>
            </article>
            <article>
                <h3>Do I need to create an account to use CryptoInfoHub?</h3>
                <p>No, you do not need to create an account to access the features of CryptoInfoHub. The platform is freely accessible to all users without any registration requirements.</p>
            </article>
            <article>
                <h3>How do I contact support if I have a question or issue?</h3>
                <p>If you have any questions or encounter any issues, you can contact our support team by emailing support@cryptoinfohub.com. We are here to help and will respond to your inquiries as soon as possible.</p>
            </article>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('footer.ejs') %>

</body>

</html>